==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zenick
<hw>Ze"nick</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
South African burrowing mammal (<spn>Suricata tetradactyla</spn>),
allied to the civets. It is grayish brown, with yellowish transverse
stripes on the back. Called also <altname>suricat</altname>.</def>
<mark>[obsolete]</mark> <note>This term is not found on the internet. It
probably refers to the <er>meerkat</er>, also called
suricate.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Zenik</ent>⟦br⟧
